{"id":779,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":779,"title":"Jeremiah 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Learn not the way of other nations—Their gods are idols and molten images—The Lord is the true and living God."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.1","order":"02.25.010.51454"},["b","1"],"Hear ye the word which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"speaketh unto you, O house of Israel:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.2","order":"02.25.010.51455"},["b","2"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Learn not the way of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"heathen"],", and be not dismayed at the signs of heaven; for the heathen are dismayed at them."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.3","order":"02.25.010.51456"},["b","3"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"customs"],"of the people",["i","are"],"vain: for",["i","one"],"cutteth a tree out of the forest, the work of the hands of the workman, with the axe."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.4","order":"02.25.010.51457"},["b","4"],"They deck it with silver and with gold; they fasten it with nails and with hammers, that it move not."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.5","order":"02.25.010.51458"},["b","5"],"They",["i","are"],"upright as the palm tree, but speak not: they must needs be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"borne"],", because they cannot go. Be not afraid of them; for they cannot do evil, neither also",["i","is it"],"in them to do good."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.6","order":"02.25.010.51459"},["b","6"],"Forasmuch as",["i","there is"],"none",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"like"],"unto thee, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; thou",["i","art"],"great, and thy name",["i","is"],"great in might."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.7","order":"02.25.010.51460"},["b","7"],"Who would not fear thee, O King of nations? for to thee doth it appertain: forasmuch as among all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"wise"],["i","men"],"of the nations, and in all their kingdoms,",["i","there is"],"none",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"like"],"unto thee."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.8","order":"02.25.010.51461"},["b","8"],"But they are altogether brutish and foolish: the stock",["i","is"],"a doctrine of vanities."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.9","order":"02.25.010.51462"},["b","9"],"Silver spread into plates is brought from Tarshish, and gold from Uphaz, the work of the workman, and of the hands of the founder: blue and purple",["i","is"],"their clothing: they",["i","are"],"all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"work"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"cunning"],["i","men."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.10","order":"02.25.010.51463"},["b","10"],"But the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"the true",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"God"],", he",["i","is"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"living God"],", and an everlasting",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"king"],": at his wrath the earth shall tremble, and the nations shall not be able to abide his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"indignation"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.11","order":"02.25.010.51464"},["b","11"],"Thus shall ye say unto them, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"gods"],"that have not made the heavens and the earth,",["i","even"],"they shall perish from the earth, and from under these heavens."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.12","order":"02.25.010.51465"},["b","12"],"He hath made the earth by his power, he hath established the world by his wisdom, and hath stretched out the heavens by his discretion."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.13","order":"02.25.010.51466"},["b","13"],"When he uttereth his voice,",["i","there is"],"a multitude of waters in the heavens, and he causeth the vapours to ascend from the ends of the earth; he maketh lightnings with rain, and bringeth forth the wind out of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"treasures"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.14","order":"02.25.010.51467"},["b","14"],"Every man is brutish in",["i","his"],"knowledge: every founder is confounded by the graven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"image"],": for his molten image",["i","is"],"falsehood, and",["i","there is"],"no breath in them."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.15","order":"02.25.010.51468"},["b","15"],"They",["i","are"],"vanity,",["i","and"],"the work of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"errors"],": in the time of their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"visitation"],"they shall perish."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.16","order":"02.25.010.51469"},["b","16"],"The portion of Jacob",["i","is"],"not like them: for he",["i","is"],"the former of all",["i","things;"],"and Israel",["i","is"],"the rod of his inheritance: The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts",["i","is"],"his name."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.17","order":"02.25.010.51470"},["b","17"],"¶Gather up thy wares out of the land, O inhabitant of the fortress."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.18","order":"02.25.010.51471"},["b","18"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Behold, I will sling out the inhabitants of the land at this once, and will distress them, that they may find",["i","it so."]],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.19","order":"02.25.010.51472"},["b","19"],"¶Woe is me for my hurt! my wound is grievous: but I said, Truly this",["i","is"],"a grief, and I must bear it."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.20","order":"02.25.010.51473"},["b","20"],"My",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"tabernacle"],"is spoiled, and all my cords are broken: my children are gone forth of me, and they",["i","are"],"not:",["i","there is"],"none to stretch forth my tent any more, and to set up my curtains."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.21","order":"02.25.010.51474"},["b","21"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"pastors"],"are become brutish, and have not sought the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": therefore they shall not prosper, and all their flocks shall be scattered."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.22","order":"02.25.010.51475"},["b","22"],"Behold, the noise of the bruit is come, and a great commotion out of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"north"],"country, to make the cities of Judah desolate,",["i","and"],"a den of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"dragons"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.23","order":"02.25.010.51476"},["b","23"],"¶O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", I know that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"way"],"of man",["i","is"],"not in himself:",["i","it is"],"not in man that walketh to direct his steps."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.24","order":"02.25.010.51477"},["b","24"],"O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"correct"],"me, but with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"judgment"],"; not in thine anger, lest thou bring me to nothing."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.25","order":"02.25.010.51478"},["b","25"],"Pour out thy fury upon the heathen that know thee not, and upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"families"],"that call not on thy name: for they have eaten up Jacob, and devoured him, and consumed him, and have made his habitation desolate."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.2a","order":"02.25.010.51479"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heathen"},"TG Heathen"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.3a","order":"02.25.010.51481"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/40.19.19-20"},"Isa. 40:19 (19–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.12"},"44:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/traditions-of-men"},"TG Traditions of Men"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.5a","order":"02.25.010.51483"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/46.7"},"Isa. 46:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.6a","order":"02.25.010.51485"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/71.19"},"Ps. 71:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.7a","order":"02.25.010.51487"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/esth/1.13"},"Esth. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.7b","order":"02.25.010.51489"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/8.10.8-10"},"Ex. 8:10 (8–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.6"},"Ps. 89:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.9a","order":"02.25.010.51491"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/115.4"},"Ps. 115:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.9b","order":"02.25.010.51493"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.84"},"D&C 124:84"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.10a","order":"02.25.010.51495"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/22.34"},"Josh. 22:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.1"},"D&C 76:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.10b","order":"02.25.010.51497"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.17"},"JS—H 1:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.10c","order":"02.25.010.51499"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"},"TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.10d","order":"02.25.010.51501"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.11a","order":"02.25.010.51503"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.13a","order":"02.25.010.51505"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"storehouses."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.14a","order":"02.25.010.51507"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.15a","order":"02.25.010.51509"},["b","15a"],["span.small","HEB"],"mockery."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.15b","order":"02.25.010.51511"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.1"},"D&C 56:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.20a","order":"02.25.010.51513"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.20"},"Jer. 4:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.21a","order":"02.25.010.51515"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shepherd"},"TG Shepherd"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.22a","order":"02.25.010.51517"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.14"},"Jer. 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.6"},"4:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.1"},"6:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.22b","order":"02.25.010.51519"},["b","22b"],["span.small","HEB"],"jackals."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.23a","order":"02.25.010.51521"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/20.24"},"Prov. 20:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.24a","order":"02.25.010.51523"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/punish"},"TG Punish"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.24b","order":"02.25.010.51525"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.16"},"Ezek. 34:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.21"},"1 Ne. 22:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.25a","order":"02.25.010.51527"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/6.4.1-4"},"Eph. 6:4 (1–4)"],"."]]}
